{% macro fixedVerificationCode(headingLevel="###") -%}
{{headingLevel}} Test Phone Numbers and Verification Codes

When submitting your app to App Store, the reviewers of your app who do not have a phone number may be unable to test your app if the only way they can log in is to use a phone number and a verification code.

It could also happen that developers of your app need to frequently log in and log out, but only limited number of verification codes can be sent out within a certain amount of time.

Therefore, we allow each app to have a **fixed phone number and verification code** for testing.

To set up your **test phone number**, go to [Dashboard](/applist.html#/apps) > **Messages** > **SMS** > **Settings** > **Misc**.
{%- endmacro %}


